> How can someone find the name of a movie extra if their name is not
> listed in the movie credits? Any ideas?

some enterprising extras place their name in the IMDB lists.  Otherwise,
you'd have to get hold of a payroll sheet. LOL.  It's rare, very rare, that
an extra gets a screen credit.  The only ones I know who have were also
stand-ins or stunts.



